---
import DefaultLayout from '../layouts/Default.astro';
import site from '~/content/site.ts';
---

<DefaultLayout>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-10">About me</h1>

    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-16">
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I'm Bruno, a Software Engineer and Tech Lead from Porto, Portugal 🇵🇹.
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            I've been building things for the web for over a decade, starting as a PHP developer in a small 5 person
            startup, growing into backend and distributed systems with Go and eventually into leading teams. These days
            I split my time between shipping code and helping engineers grow.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
            I work primarily with <strong>Golang</strong> and <strong>TypeScript/Node.js</strong>, though I don't
            consider myself tied to any particular stack. I pick whatever fits the problem best. My focus is backend
            engineering, but I'm comfortable across the stack when needed.
          </p>
        </p>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-neutral-800">What Drives Me</h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            I care about well-crafted systems, clean APIs, good observability, and teams that ship with confidence, but
            more importantly, systems that solve real problems, for individuals and businesses.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Beyond software, I'm interested in all areas of STEM, from Phycology, to BioTech. I believe the most
            interesting problems happen at the intersection of disciplines.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            A curious mind is a developer's most underrated asset. I try to keep learning something new constantly,
            inside and outside tech.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            I'm a proponent of the open web and decentralization: protocols over platforms, interoperability over
            lock-in, communities over corporations.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
            I'm skeptical of walled gardens and centralized platforms that trade user freedom for convenience, and I try
            to support open alternatives wherever I can. I miss the spirit of the early internet days, where curiosity,
            creativity and openness were at the center stage. I try to do my small part to keep that ideas alive.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-neutral-800">Outside Work</h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            I enjoy sports, watching TV series and anime, and spending time with friends over a good meal.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
            I also contribute to open source, mostly small tools and libraries that solve a personal itch, which you can
            find on
            <a
              href={site.social.github}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 underline"
            >
              GitHub
            </a>. When I have something worth sharing, I write about it on <a
              href="/blog"
              class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 underline"
            >
              my blog
            </a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</DefaultLayout>
